metadata.description:
Heart Growth ll
To me this image is powerful in so many ways. Having a healthy heart is essential to well being. To have heart in life brings adventure and accomplishments. A big heart, a loving heart, a caring heart is the most important of them all. Try to listen and understand people. Be caring and open to their situation. Itâ€™s easy to miss the beauty that exists in our differences. Let all the experiences you have help your heart grow big, happy and healthy.
